Fusion Nclusion is a collective of wedding professionals that specialize in luxury, cultural weddings. The collective was founded by Denise of Denise Lillie Engagements in February 2020 in Northern California and now expands Worldwide. We strive to inspire, educate, and celebrate each other while promoting diversity within the wedding industry.

Have you heard our BIG. HUGE. NEWS!!! 🎉🧡
At the start of 2023, we officially expanded the Blissful Events bubble!!!! 
We are offering DJ services, photo booths and up lighting!! 🎶🧡🎉

What does all of this mean? Since 2007 when I started Blissful Events, the mission has been to give my clients the best and most fun and relaxing wedding planning experience they could ever ask for. In 2017 when the wine country wild fires happened, this mission became so much embedded in the Blissful Events culture. But this time, we had a deeper appreciation and honor that we also get to create jobs for others in our community. 

So we launched these amazing new services to really complete our mission of giving our clients the best experience possible and by making it even more fun and easy with bundling more fun experiences together. All while continuing to create more opportunities in our community. 

We are SO proud and honored that we get to do what we do for a living. AND we get to do it wish such amazing pros by our side! 

For more info, link is in the bio. 

Let’s party!! 🥳🎉🍾
